import React from 'react'

import RoundedButton from '../../../global/buttons/RoundedButton'

import './css/SelectForm.scss'

const SelectForm = (props) => {
    return (
        <>
            <RoundedButton
                button_CLASSNAME={'blue_ROUNDEDBUTTON'}
                button_ID={'languages_header_BUTTON'}
                span_CLASSNAME={'p-medium'}
                button_TEXT={'Rent'}
                Arrow002={true}
            />
            <button
                type='button'
                id='rent_LI'
                className='p-medium'
            >
                Rent
            </button>
            <button
                type='button'
                id='rentOut_LI'
                className='p-medium'
            >
                Rent out
            </button>
        </>
    )
}

export default SelectForm
